text: Jomana Elmaghrabi (born 21 June 1995) is an Egyptian synchronised swimmer. She competed in the team event at the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Egyptian synchronized swimmers Category:Olympic synchronized swimmers of Egypt Category:Synchronized swimmers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
